And just the idea of being locked out of my Gmail.

00:18:34.020 --> 00:18:37.600
I mean, just stop and think about how much of your life is in your Gmail inbox.

00:18:37.920 --> 00:18:38.680
How long have you had yours?

00:18:39.000 --> 00:18:39.440
15 years.

