And, not even including the fact that everything that an AI does by its very nature is derivative of something that's actually being done before.

00:51:38.800 --> 00:51:41.640
So, you're never getting anything truly new and truly revolutionary.

00:51:42.520 --> 00:51:48.360
When it comes to, like, boring, menial tasks, like figuring out why my server's slow, have at it.

