This is the commands you run to, like, create the external network and then here's the settings and all the compose files.

00:52:30.740 --> 00:52:32.880
You restart them in this order so stuff doesn't break.

00:52:32.880 --> 00:52:33.920
I'm like, wow, okay.

00:52:33.920 --> 00:52:48.280
If you know just enough to be dangerous on a topic and you can guide it through the hallucinations that it does, it makes you incredibly powerful and so, for that reason, at least for the foreseeable future, I don't think it's going to replace, you know,

