So I use it for things like I have a local LLM running on my Mac.

00:58:42.680 --> 00:58:43.000
Oh, yeah.

00:58:43.360 --> 00:58:56.180
And then if I'm at the coffee shop, then I just make sure I'm on the Tailscale network and I can still run apps that talk to my OpenAI API over my self-hosted LLM as if it was running on my laptop, but it's not, right?

00:58:56.240 --> 00:58:56.400
